        <h1 class="about__title">This is our <br>Story</h1>

        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">

                <img src="/img/about-1-small.png" alt="" class="card-img u-mb-lrg">
                <div class="card-title">
                    <h4>Foundation</h4>
                </div>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">

                <div class="card-item card-text">
                    Soul Notes LC London was founded in 2023, a intimate gap was being ignored that
